{"tid":1823511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門街坊入","createTime":"2020-01-13T17:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T18:11:58.000Z","uid":294957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"082cb346e2de4f1b3f54a42de587a41b983789e1","tid":1823511,"uid":294957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fJW1UzxQ63A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfJW1UzxQ63A&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=af1add74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fJW1UzxQ63A</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好撳入去</span></span></span><br />\n內容大要：聽日3點大媽照舊開檔，次次都咁少人睇死你地班屯門人<br />\n<br />\n今日班老同大媽出手打人，班狗到場結果原告變被告，<br />\n今日議員如常在 #屯門公園 當值。當時張可森助理為了保護林明恩，於是站在兩者之間，避免林明恩被滋擾。防暴警到場後，突然將助理、一名大媽和一名大叔帶到一邊問話，再將該名助理及大叔帶走，聲稱是帶回警署協助調查。然而一眾區議員到青山警署了解後，竟得知該名助理被警方以涉嫌打人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n班大媽同鹹濕伯父已經無法無天，康文一直無執過法，光復屯公已經唔係一朝一夕嘅事，希望各位屯門街坊團結，對抗大媽！<br />\n<br />\n屯門人！3點屯公1.2億橋集合"},{"pid":"9218942dca10a42ef9dc199471148eaed51506eb","tid":1823511,"uid":313928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3019c4461409d9256c0f652052e2ae5e2c703b2e","tid":1823511,"uid":313928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:01:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e56a362e4596e2e9eb86c54a9300ce23c6978935","tid":1823511,"uid":313928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44c2f1fed3913ddc3abb3eae751c13e687593098","tid":1823511,"uid":313928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"641517893b9bee94da6eec7032ec74fa9095cb8d","tid":1823511,"uid":313928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T18:07:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e2e57952fb0fd1b338cc115a0c66dc36c47c4f2","tid":1823511,"uid":313928,"